sequenceDiagram
participant Client
participant API
participant Facade as HBnBFacade
participant User
participant UserRepo as UserRepository
participant DB as Database

Client->>API: POST /users (user data)
API->>Facade: create_user(data)
Facade->>User: new User(data)
Facade->>UserRepo: save(user)
UserRepo->>DB: INSERT user
DB-->>UserRepo: OK
UserRepo-->>Facade: user saved
Facade-->>API: success response
API-->>Client: 201 Created
